Invocation Name: workout motivation
des:
Lacking motivation to get back into the gym?
Back in the gym already but feel stagnated?
Or maybe you’re just looking for new inspiration for a the new year.
Whatever your situation, reading words of wisdom from successful people can be super-inspiring.
Start your day with an inspirational list of quotes. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
